            <p>We have many different styles of packaging that cater to our products. Choosing an easy-to-use packaging style will make all of it comfortable for the customers. Among some of the standard styles for custom boxes, here are some of those provided by Citi Packaging:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Gable Boxes:</strong> Perfect for easy carrying, these boxes feature a distinctive handle design, making them ideal for takeout food, party favors, and gifts.</li>
                <li><strong>Window Die-Cut Boxes:</strong> These boxes are designed with clear PVC windows that allow customers to view the products inside. This feature not only protects the contents from dust and moisture but also entices buyers by showcasing the product.</li>
